data.description:
This ranch style 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home sitting on just over a quarter of an acre offers plenty of living areas, large bedrooms, covered porches and oversized backyard.
The HVAC system was replaced in 2021 and kitchen was updated with new countertops, painted cabinets and quartz countertops. 
Check out this home today!
Seller will be getting a plumber report and updating sellers disclosure. 
Multiple offers received . No more showings as of 5-7-22 8pm . Seller will review offers at 10am 5-8-22
